race.comment: DOMINANT FORCE (5) drops right back in grade today following a 1.5L defeat in stronger company 11 days ago. She finished off strongly there from the back of a small field and the rise to 1500m looks up her alley. Drawn to hold a spot today and she can knock over this maiden if she can run up to her form. LATORIO (2) turned in a strong effort at Northam last start when beaten 2.1L over the mile journey. Form out of that has been solid and she wasn't beaten too far as favourite here two starts ago. Ticks a few boxes and can go one better this time around. TRAILER TRUCK (4) felt the pinch late last start over 1400m at Northam but the winner of that race has since won again on Melbourne Cup Day at Ascot. Tongue Tie goes on now and the inside draw is a big tick. Can give them something to chase. ROSENTREA (3) is a long-time maiden but has turned in some sound performances recently. Drops back a level today and has claims. LUKA MAGIC (1) is worth including on debut.
